text: 1:33:00 You know what's hilarious? Hololive Members setting records after records in Fall Guys. Getting the Last Stage Crown is no easy task (except for Okayu... getting it at Lvl 3 LoL) but Getting your Opponent Team Zero is no easy task as well. Didn't imagine I'd witness it twice. 1st with Matsuri's 15-0 during her Soccer Team battle then this one, then there's also Pekora's 56 reduced to 8 First Round elimination straight right to Finals. And her reaching the Final Round 3x times straight and being 1st place (1st to be eliminated) A-Ha↗️Ha↘️Ha↗️Ha↘️Ha↗️Ha↘️Ha↗️
